DCF...Dreams That NEVER Die... 
 ~~754boy's Ultimate DOOM DC Mega Collection~~

754boy is back again with a DCF exclusive release!!! I've compiled all the greatest Doom mods and total conversions and have released them in one tidy package. Included in the compilation is: 

Doom
Doom II 
Final Doom addons 

Wolfenstein Original
Wolfenstein Nocturnal Missions
Wolfenstein Spear of Destiny

Eternal Mod 
Quake Doom
Batman Doom 
Biowar Mod
Blood Mod 
Doom 2 Extreme
The Darkening 2 mod 
DOOM 64 Mod 
Pheonix Weapons Mod 
Duke Nuke 3D TC 
Earth Mod 
Fist Full of Doom 
Goldeneye 64 TC 
Heretic TC
Hell Revealed II mod
Star Trek Mod 
Twilight Warrior TC 
Ultimate Simpsons Doom Mod

So much DOOM that you'll be busy for weeks on end. Some of the mods take a little time to load so be patient and enjoy. I realize that I haven't included every know Doom mod, just some good ones that I could get to work. Who knows......maybe there will be a part 2 to this compilation with even more cool mods :D......there most likely will ;)

I have also included in the rar file HIGH RESOLUTION cd covers for those who like to keep their games looking as good as they play. The covers were done by DCF member Willis, who also requested that I do the release in the first place :)

For more info on DoomDC, visit the homepage at http://www.doomdc.tk

For more info on all the mods, visit the Doom Wad Station at http://www.doomwadstation.com

Enjoy this great release and please keep this goodie seeded!!!!